  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/839540/extras/b926d80b91a5a5b5a55e9ec4ebdf78fc.avif?t=1643380212\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>Welcome to Electroquest: Resistance is Futile! This brainteaser is a good opportunity to check your knowledge of electrical engineering and improve your logical thinking. Test your engineering skills and try to put all the elements of an electric circuit in the right places.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/839540/extras/6f31c0a4747cd22f6ccd12dcfef6665c.avif?t=1643380212\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>Your goal is to place all the elements in a way to get them connected into a proper line circuit system. Let there be light!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/839540/extras/6a1d6f93c8813acd67e94a2ca84348e3.avif?t=1643380212\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 challenging levels to beat;<br></li><li>А great test for your knowledge of electrical engineering.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/839540/extras/e2252bd180397903b0de69a41f0cc10a.avif?t=1643380212\" width=600 height=340 /></span>",
